zi_company_description__c: Buyee is a global E-Commerce service that allows customers living outside of Japan to purchase items from Japanese EC Sites. Buyee purchases the items in proxy and will ship the items overseas to the customer. It uses modern technology including machine learning to provide a service that is save, convenient and easy to understand. Buyee has over 1 million users (as of October 2019). Buyee receives a lot of recognition from its users for its variety of methods for payment and shipping, its ability to consolidate items from several EC sites into one package and its high-grade quality inspection and shipping protection services.
